long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily convert nautical miles to miles or kilometers, wherever you are browsing on the web. Handy, as it allows you to better estimate the duration of the ferry crossing while exploring ferry routes.

Here's how it works:

1. Download the free Chrome extension and activate it in your bookmarks bar.
2. Come across nautical miles anywhere on the web? Click on the extension.
3. Enter the nautical miles and press Convert.
4. View the distance in kilometers and miles.
